cff-version: 1.2.0
title: >-
  Bayesian Hyperparameter Optimization of SVM with TPE
  for Stress Detection in Spanish Social Media
message: >-
  If you use this software or its results, please cite the
  associated CIT 2026 paper (Springer LNNS) using the
  preferred-citation entry below.
